TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed FtpStatusCode extends System.Enum

summary.span: 指定为文件传输协议 (FTP) 操作返回的状态代码。

span.span: Specifies the status codes returned for a File Transfer Protocol (FTP) operation.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 枚举定义中返回的值属性。The enumeration defines the values returned in the property. 有关 FTP 服务器状态代码的其他信息，请参阅[RFC 959:"文件传输协议"中，部分 4.2:"FTP 回复"](https://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc959.txt)。For additional information about FTP server status codes, see [RFC 959: "File Transfer Protocol", Section 4.2: "FTP Replies"](https://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc959.txt). ## Examples 下面的代码示例发送 FTP 请求以 FTP 服务器上创建一个新目录，并检查响应中返回的状态代码。The following code example sends an FTP request to make a new directory on an FTP server and checks the status code returned in the response. [!code-cpp[NclFtpClient#22](~/samples/snippets/cpp/VS_Snippets_Remoting/NCLFtpClient/CPP/ftptests.cpp#22)] [!code-csharp[NclFtpClient#22](~/samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_Remoting/NCLFtpClient/CS/ftptests.cs#22)]
